      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "ティルピッツに誘われて、母港のはずれにある高台にやってきた。",
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "すまない。こんなところまで付き合ってもらって。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "実はあなたと一緒に見たいものがある。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "content": "北極星？",
          "flag": 1
        }
      ],
      "say": "ティルピッツは空に輝く「それ」を指さした。",
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "そう、Polarstem（北極星）。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "この星を見るたびに、あの時――母港に引きこもって、「艦隊にいるだけ」がすべての自分を思い出す。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "寒さも孤独も慣れて、なにも感じず、無為に過ごし続けた日々。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "そして戦果一つも得られず、絶望の煙に覆われる港の空を眺めながら破滅を迎える最後。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "おかしくて、虚しいだけの命（いのち）だと思わないか。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "……",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "今は、違う。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "触れ合う楽しさ、そばに居てくれている安心感。この温もりは寒さも孤独も融かしてくれた。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "「孤独なる北欧の女王」はいまや孤独ではない。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "願わくば、鏡の中の――夢の中の私も、こうして幸せに……",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "……少し疲れたのかしら。",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "肩に隣に座っている彼女からの重みを感じた。",
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "ねえ、ちょっとだけ寄り添ってもいいかな…？",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "say": "指揮官の温もり、もう少し感じさせてほしい…",
      "actor": 405020,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "囁きにも近しい、優しい声が耳元で響く。",
      "bgName": "bg_night"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "彼女にはずっと、優しくあってほしい。",
      "blackBg": true,
